PrecisAuthority to members of the Canadian Forces to accept and wear the United Nations Transitional Authority in Cambodia (UNTAC) Medal in recognition of honourable service with the United Nations Transitional Authority in Cambodia and that the Medal follow the United Nations Protection Force (UNPROFOR) Medal in the order of Precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
